## Impact Rules

- **DedgeAuth.Client change** → `Build-And-Publish-ALL.ps1` (all apps need updated DLL)
- **DedgeAuth wwwroot change** → rebuild DedgeAuth only (consumers fetch via proxy)
- **Tenant branding** → update `tenants` table only, no rebuild
- **Deploy template change** → run `IIS-DeployApp\_deploy.ps1` to sync to servers
